name: Blk Orchid - Blk Orchid ft. Nick. -I'll Go (Remix)

metadata.description:
3x Juno Nominated producer, artist and songwriter Blk Orchid brings this special 1 year anniversary Remix of her hit, I'll Go. Featuring amazing rapper Nick. who brings a whole new vibe and perspective to this incredible track. Holders of this limited edition NFT will receive acccess to the token gated I'll Go Tellie site which includes downloads of the orginal song and demos,lyrics, cover art and more. the recipent of the Golden EGG will have a special edition visualizer from the I'll Go Collection on Opensea.

This song has deep meaning, on the outside it speaks about love, but Blk Orchid is singing as AI personified, have we let technology become too controlling in our lives where it can have feelings, like love?


I'll Go Remix ft Nick.
Produced By Blk Orchid
Mixed and Mastered by Austin Lee of Midnight Studios
